data.title: Spookiz
data.synopsis:
When night falls and the human kids from Freemont Elementary have all gone home, these wacky monsters creep out for their own slapstick adventures. Together, a vain Vampire, a happy-go-lucky Goblin, a smelly Zombie, a snuggly Frankenstein and a mischievous Ghost share a common bond and friendship in their adventures at night school.

(Source: Amazon Prime)
